---
title: Double Striploin Steaks and Sun-Dried Tomato Cream Sauce with Roasted Potatoes and Walnut-Topped Asparagus
description: Break out the fine china to feast tonight! Tender steaks are topped with creamy, umami-rich sun-dried tomato cream sauce in this lick-the-plate-clean dish. Walnuts, Parmesan and asparagus make the perfect trio to balance out this luxe meal.
